#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into "
"a tool to manage your entire workflow."
msgstr ""
"Odoo està totalment integrat en una aplicació. Descarrega'l per convertir el "
"teu telèfon en una eina per gestionar el flux de treball sencer."

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers endless customization possibilities for your cake shop:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo t'ofereix una infinitat de possibilitats per a la teva pastisseria:"

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Aquesta és només una vista general de les funcionalitats incloses al paquet. "
"No dubtis a afegir noves aplicacions, eliminar/modificar les dades demo i "
